Intoxicating and arresting this luxury scent is concocted for the self-assured and radiant woman who enraptures the crowd. Indulging her deep-rooted desires and nursing her innocent narcissism Guess Seductive makes an indelible mark. Created by perfumer Veronique Nyberg this hypnotic Eau De Toilette is made for the trend-setting brand of Guess.

The top note opens with a refreshing spark redolent with citrusy and sweet hints of bergamot tart and tangy notes of blackcurrant along with the sweet and refined hints of pear. Moving into the heart we can get a delectable aroma that mixes fragrant and bitter notes of orris root distinct notes of jasmineÂ and welcoming notes of African orange flower. Culminating into a base note of rich and creamy hints of vanilla the incense like aroma of olibanum along with silky and woody notes of cashmere wood. Interlacing exotic accords that is meant to beguile and entice this perfume is perfect for a romantic night out. This scent is encased within a solid glass cuboid decorated with a triangular black badge bearing the name and a petite gold chain dangling from the neck. Topped with a transparent crown the pale gold hue of this perfume glows through the glass. Kohl-rimmed eyes sky-high stilettos cascading hair ruby-red lips a spritz of Guess Seductive and scream your presence without uttering a word.

A scent for that demure woman whose soft-spoken ways and serene aura leave you helplessly spellbound. Leaving a trail of devoted admirers along with a waft of Guess she walks in bashful grace oozing an old-world charm. Created by perfumer Maurice Roucel this enticing Eau De Parfum is made for the celebrated brand of Guess.

The top note opens with the refreshing scent of green apple entangled with tart wild strawberry sweet citrusy bergamot and honeyed notes of tangerine. Followed by a beguiling heart luscious notes of peach with banana toned ylang-ylang clean notes of lily of the valley tangy red berries waxy lemony magnolia peppery freesia exotic jasmine and fresh peony make up a lovely aroma. Descending into a heavenly dry down the base note combines warm cedar organic oakmoss soothing and heavy hints of musk with smoky resinous amber. An intriguing amalgamation of accords you can wear this luxury perfume at any time of the day. The flacon boasts of a contemporary design that combines the sleek elegance of steel against clear and classic glass. Shaped to form the letter G the mauve coloured fragrance can be seen floating against the glass. Take a guess and go for a wonderful addition to your beauty cabinet.

Fruity and floral Guess by Marciano enthralls the senses through an interplay of myriad deeply enigmatic notes. Glamorous and seductive the confident Guess woman knows what she wants. This delightfully sultry luxury Eau de Perfume unites a timeless classic elegance with contemporary chic to create a harmonious and potent symphony.

Created by perfumer Barbara Zoebelein Guess derives its allure from the zesty top note of curacao orange star fruit and cardamom seeds which is delicately blended with the dulcet tones of peony jasmine and sweet honeysuckle. An earthy base note of woody accords and enchanting vanilla infuses a subtle intensity to the floral rhythm. The allure of this feminine aroma perfectly complements the charm of a first date. Encased in a gold vial of pure opulence and glamour Guess by Marciano is certainly for the woman who always gets what she wants.
